e":"2019-07-31T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de52034d47b0ddde206021b59ad42725a645b05a","tid":1391360,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"人地係三分二民眾支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128942a18adfd377c04db75a723a4e60f07316e9","tid":1391360,"uid":240250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"搵歐洲呢d高級人種同東亞病夫比？<br />\n太睇得起香港人，香港人有人地一半咁夠薑就唔會搞到而家咁<br />\n睇死你班垃圾唔敢罷工，85有一成人罷到工我切乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57781aaf801dace60029b0334d9467461cc6b8a4","tid":1391360,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de52034d47b0ddde206021b59ad42725a645b05a","tid":1391360,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"人地係三分二民眾支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"成班醫護狗罷都未罷就話唔罷得 跟本就係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院罷工會唔會先係真正有用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344819</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n&lt;醫護人員的心聲&gt; 正因為醫護人員要堅守崗位，我地懇請更多香港市民代我地參與罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d30056c6e8fc87559ac8f81318c728d8c65e703e","tid":1391360,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c832dbb8fc864cb9126f99b3ad5243858b1fe2","tid":1391360,"uid":263219